<seg id=1> Military Accidents Frequently Occur in South Korea, Opposition Demands Foreign Minister to Resign </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> (Reuters, Seoul) South Korean opposition parties yesterday demanded Defence Minister Chun Yong-taek to design, because before this, the troops caused several accidents, including launching armed missiles and star shells to civilian areas. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Korean officials said that the latest accident was that a military exercise went wrong at dawn yesterday: the case of a star shell broke through two walls of an old woman's house. </seg>
<seg id=4> The old woman's house was close to where the fragments fell after the missile exploded two days ago. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> Navy officials said that the star shell launched by Korean marines shot even farther than expected, falling to the civil house in Jinpu. </seg>
<seg id=6> Jinpu is to the west of Seoul. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> Opposition Grand National Party made a statement saying, "Defence Minister Chun Yong-taek must immediately resign, otherwise (President Kim Dae-jung) must dismiss him." </seg>
<seg id=8> A government that does not fear the people is not the one of the people." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=9> The statement said, "Chun Yong-taek is trying to hold on to his seat with just a word of apology ... This is an act of utter arrogance." </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=10> The day before yesterday Defence Ministry apologized for the missile launching accident. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=11> Navy officials said that the case of the star shell entered the bath room after breaking through two walls. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=12> He said that the old woman aged 83 was receiving treatment in a nearby hospital for being overfrightened. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=13> Last Friday Korean troops accidentally launched a ground-to-air missile, which exploded in the mid-air and caused injuries of at least three civilians. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=14> An official from Defence Ministry said that military technical staff at an air force base in the western port city of Inchon while checking weapons, accidentally launched the missile. </seg>
<seg id=15> Inchon is 40 kms away from the line dividing the two Koreas. </seg>
</p>
